title: Akin Gumpapalooza 2015
description: Please join Akin Gump’s Intellectual Property practice to partake in libations, food and fun featuring a live performance from last year's SXSW Rock Band of the Year Quiet Company!

title: Animal Planet's Next Cat Star Party
description: Animal Planet & AT&T are on the search to find America’s Next Cat Star. COME TO THE PURRRRTY on Sunday, March 15th at Cedar Street Courtyard where the finalists will be revealed… giving party goers the first chance to vote for America’s Next Cat Star while dancing the night away with Austin’s favorite 80’s band, The Spazmatics #SxCATSTAR.

title: The Beatport House
description: Celebrate the relaunch of Beatport - the home of electronic music - at the intersection of tech and music, featuring DJ sets, backyard chats with industry power players, refreshments, recharging, and more. Daily schedule: btprt.dj/sxsw.
